Micro-ondes is based in Rhone-Alpes, Geneva Switzerland. It specializes in the field of electromagnetic waves high and low frequencies measurement with technical instruments and advice on sites.

Electricity, GSM, UMTS (3G) mobile phone, relay antenna, WiFi, WiMAX, DECT, radar, satellite, Bluetooth, etc, generate electromagnetic fields. These fields may have biological effects to our bodies.

